Full Description: buzzl is a brand new type of social platform. Content within buzzl is unique because it is all driven by location. Activity within the app also generates 'buzz' for each user, which they can then spend on local places and events to show their support. Speaking of events, buzzl also has integrated location-based chat for every event that is created. This chat gives attendees a place to look for by-the-minute announcements, and connect with other attendees to network, ask questions, or make new friends. Finally, we have created an entirely new technology we call buzzlBox. Think of Drop Box, but all the stored data has physical coordinates tied to it. This means you can serve up contextual information for a user's surroundings. Maps, menus, and more are all easily accessible and businesses can even save money by not printing those items anymore. Description: Inter-Family Office Synergy
Full Description: PACTUM PARTNERS was founded on the understanding that sophisticated family offices, aligned through shared missions, visions, and values, would benefit from a partner dedicated to fostering co-investment and peer collaboration. Family Offices, in ever increasing numbers, leverage their entrepreneurial DNA in the pursuit of direct investments. Offices struggle to review proposed investments due to a lack of trust, experience, staff, and/or time. The challenges, associated with the rise in direct investments, encourage a desire for co- investment with like-minded entities. A misalignment in values and horizons, alongside an environment of high fees, drives family offices from traditional investments in public equities and fund structures. High standards with regards to privacy, discretion, and security further limit potential strategic partners. We believe that the best long-term partner for family offices are other family offices. Uniquely capable of leveraging their significant shared expertise, capital, and influence, inter-family office partnerships provide an attractive alternative to traditional fund managers by operating with greater control and flexibility without facing limiting time horizons, high fees, and regulatory restrictions. The opportunity for cross-collaboration often presents itself beyond the traditional realm of capital allocation.

Description: ReEntry Capital is a venture capital firm.
Full Description: ReEntry Capital is a pioneering venture capital firm and accelerator program specifically aimed at supporting and empowering justice-involved founders. Born out of the founder's own experience with the justice system, ReEntry Capital seeks to bridge the resource gap for these entrepreneurs and challenge societal biases. Our approach centers on backing startups founded by individuals who have been impacted by the justice system. We believe that their unique insights, resilience, and creativity make them poised for success, and we're dedicated to giving them the support they need to unlock their full potential. Our focus spans across various sectors, fostering innovation and driving positive social impact. The ReEntry Capital Accelerator program provides intensive mentoring, resources, and support to enable these founders to transform their ideas into reality. Post-acceleration, ReEntry Capital also offers a fund to further support these startups, helping them scale and thrive in their respective markets. Our long-term goal is to challenge and change the narrative around justice-involved individuals. By supporting their entrepreneurial journey, we aim to demonstrate the untapped potential within this often overlooked population and encourage more inclusive entrepreneurship ecosystems. In addition to our accelerator and fund, ReEntry Capital is also committed to advocacy and education. We work to raise awareness about the systemic barriers justice-involved individuals face and promote policies and practices that support their reintegration into society. By combining venture capital with social impact, ReEntry Capital is working to create a more equitable entrepreneurial landscape. Lastly, ReEntry Capital is also exploring strategic partnerships and initiatives that align with our mission.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Seattle Area, West Coast, Western US
